metadata.name: Zen fossil card #3
metadata.description:
Along our journey, we embody the legacy of the inherited experiences & wisdom from those who came before us. And so will we.
These are the bones of the New Earth we are creating. An always-perfect-art-in-progress…

«Life has no opposite. The opposite of death is birth. Life is eternal.»  

Pick your card from this minimalist zen fossil deck to remind you about the intrinsic connection between yourself and each and every other being in the circle of life. You’re never alone in the journey.
Let it surprise you with 9 different illustrations, 12 colours, several frames, 5 background textures and a lovely 感激高明 stamp.

感激谦高明
gratitud, humildad, sabiduría
gratitude, humbleness, wisdom

May it find you at peace. ♡
Luz Art

PS, in the seal «谦» (modesty) stood aside ;)

metadata.name: Onward, to Hy Breasail #8
metadata.description:
Hy Breasail was an island that only existed on the antique maps.
According to belief, there was a fantastic island that roamed the ocean and was completely covered in mists. Every seven years, the mists dissipated and the land could be seen by human eyes, but never reached.

With this project, I wanted to remember this history, creating maps that never existed before, a paper cartography, where sometimes it is blurred or glitched, because of the fog that haunts the island.

This project have 2 predominant colors + 2 blendModes, wich can invert the colors or change, a total of 4 colors pallettes.

It takes a little time to render completely (10 seconds aprox.), but after it has rendered all the base art, the textures are loaded.

Styles can vary from grids, horizontal divisions, vertical divisions, and the clean aspect, without glitching.


- open in live view for a better experience.


This is a project in p5.js

Omar Lobato Neto,
02/06/2022.

metadata.name: Stereo Print #35
metadata.description:
Generative audio painted on canvas. Tap to see and hear the composition in real time.

Stereo Print is my second collection in the paint-with-sound genre. Each mint has uniquely generated two-channel audio in the style of jazz, distortion, chimes, tones, space, or noise. The piece's visual texture is sourced directly from the audio signal. The raw waveforms are layered, masked, and transformed to produce the final composition.

Made with Web Audio and p5js. Idlebit, 2022.
